  "id": "RAW_534d4d",
  "title": "夸克生成千万份志愿报告背后：一个 Agent 应用“深度落地”的真实样本",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&mid=2247614834&idx=1&sn=e7ac5c4207e90e38b19daeae9f249716",
  "date": "2025-07-03 05:19:44",
