  "content": "\n \n \n  <h1 class=\"rich_media_title \" id=\"activity-name\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 14px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: 500; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.4; user-select: text; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><br></h1>\n  <div class=\"rich_media_content js_underline_content autoTypeSetting24psection fix_apple_default_style\" id=\"js_content\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 17px; overflow: hidden; text-align: justify; position: relative; z-index: 0; user-select: text; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px;\">\n   <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px 0px 30px; padding: 0px 8px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; letter-spacing: inherit; text-align: start; background: none; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ff87565b-b3fa-458f-6641-cf95c21f0200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100131172\" data-original-style=\"width:100%;\" data-index=\"1\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/12f82553-5bab-4336-a565-12757e039b00/public\" _width=\"100%\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"0\" data-fail=\"0\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 661px !important; visibility: visible !important;\">\n    </section>\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: inherit; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 13px; line-height: 21px; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">作者</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(221, 221, 221); visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">｜</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: inherit; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">辛峰</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">邮箱</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(221, 221, 221); visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">｜</span><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: inherit; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">xf@pingwest.com</span>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这个夏天，一个数据不仅在AI圈内引起了关注，更牵动了千万中国家庭的心：不到一个月，超过1000万份详尽的高考志愿报告，由一个具备深度研究能力的Agent免费生成。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这不是一次技术演示，而是一项直接关系到未来的高风险服务。提供这项服务的，是阿里的夸克。在一次内部技术沟通会上，夸克算法负责人蒋冠军将志愿报告定义为“是夸克深度研究技术的一次重要实践” 。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这引出了一个值得探讨的问题，当许多AI应用还停留在看似万能但可能不可靠的阶段时，夸克是如何在一个零容错的场景里，实现大规模深度落地的？它的实践，为我们提供了一个观察AI如何从玩具走向工具再进化为智能助手的真实样本。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">用户具体是如何与这个Agent互动的呢？过程十分简单，用户输入分数等基本信息后，用日常说话的方式告诉Agent自己的想法，比如想去哪个城市、对什么专业感兴趣。Agent随后会生成一份包含完整志愿表的深度报告。用户可以反复修改想法，多次生成报告，夸克方面提到，有用户甚至生成了一百多份报告来辅助决策。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; letter-spacing: inherit; text-align: start; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a92746b2-53c6-4a8d-5da7-8d4a6b69f300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder_err\" data-ratio=\"0.72\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"750\" height=\"1474\" width=\"2048\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"405\" data-imgfileid=\"100131169\" data-original-style=\"border:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;width:100%;letter-spacing:inherit;\" data-index=\"2\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVQImWNgYGBgAAAABQABh6FO1AAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\" _width=\"100%\" alt=\"图片\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 8px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; letter-spacing: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E %3Cpath d='M13.3033 5.18198C13.4986 4.98672 13.4986 4.67014 13.3033 4.47487L10.8284 2L9.9799 2.84853L11.1692 4.03784C6.58809 4.45713 3 8.30954 3 13C3 17.9706 7.02944 22 12 22C16.9706 22 21 17.9706 21 13C21 10.5147 19.9926 8.26472 18.364 6.63604L17.5154 7.48457C18.9696 8.93869 19.8 10.9021 19.8 13C19.8 17.3078 16.3078 20.8 12 20.8C7.69218 20.8 4.2 17.3078 4.2 13C4.2 8.83411 7.46585 5.43101 11.5769 5.21128L9.9799 6.80833L10.8284 7.65685L13.3033 5.18198Z' fill='%23000000' fill-opacity='0.55'/%3E %3C/svg%3E &quot;) 50% 50% / 20px no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(247, 247, 247) !important; height: 475.92px !important; width: 661px !important;\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; letter-spacing: inherit; text-align: start; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: -30px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: 16px; color: transparent; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3); overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">1</span></p>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; font-weight: bold; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: inherit; color: rgb(55, 80, 114); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">Agent如何成为一个“靠谱”的决策顾问？</strong></p>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">每年高考后，志愿填报的复杂性都会被重新讨论。近3000所高校、超过2000个专业，构成了一个巨大的信息迷宫 。近几年，随着“张雪峰”等志愿填报专家的走红，也反映了市场的核心痛点，考生和家长缺的不仅是信息，更是一个能帮忙做复杂决策的可信顾问，这也催生了一个鱼龙混杂的志愿填报服务行业。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">AI能成为这个顾问吗？蒋冠军的看法很坦诚，“当前这个阶段，AI肯定是替代不了考生自己的决策” 。那么，夸克要做的，或者说AI现阶段能做到的是什么？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">答案或许不是替代，而是成为一个靠谱的辅助决策系统。所谓的靠谱，体现在它如何处理现实世界中那些模糊、甚至矛盾的复杂需求上。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">比如，当用户的理想与现实冲突时。一个常见的需求是“想留在本省的好城市，但分数只够得上外省的985院校” 。一个简单的工具可能会陷入逻辑死循环，但夸克的Agent会尝试像真人顾问一样权衡，它可能会主动拓宽选项，为你展示“省外985”和“省内顶尖211”各自的利弊，将决策权交还给你 。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">更有挑战性的是当用户的需求本身就自相矛盾。夸克高考算法负责人唐亮提到了一个典型场景，“数学成绩差，但想报考计算机” 。这背后是学生对专业要求的不了解。此时，一个负责任的Agent不应盲目执行指令，而是会触发一个需求澄清流程，温和地提示其中的风险，并引导用户探索更适合的选项 。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">处理复杂场景的能力让AI从一个冰冷的执行机器，向一个能与人商量、值得参考的顾问角色迈进了一步。而要实现这一切，靠的不是单一的模型技巧，而是在后台，一套笨重但扎实的系统工程。</span></p>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; letter-spacing: inherit; text-align: start; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: -30px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: 16px; color: transparent; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3); overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">1</span></p>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; font-weight: bold; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: inherit; color: rgb(55, 80, 114); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“笨功夫”与“精细活”</strong></p>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“信任”是Agent在严肃场景落地的基石。夸克构建信任的方式，可以归结为两种，一种是下笨功夫，另一种是做精细活。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">笨功夫下在了数据上。夸克做了几件脏活累活，他们搜集了8657个权威站点进行分级，将超过10万份PDF、Word等非标内容数字化，并组织上百人团队对关键数据进行人工校验，以确保准确率达到“4个9”（99.99%）的水平。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这些工作听起来没有算法那么炫酷，但它们共同构成了一个高可信度的知识库，是模型能做出正确判断的前提。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">而精细活则体现在模型的调校上，必须为其注入垂直场景的灵魂 。夸克为此设计的训练范式，层层递进：整个过程始于SFT（监督微调），让模型学习上万条真实专家的推理逻辑，学会像专家那样去分析问题、组织语言 。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">在此基础上，利用RLVR（可验证奖励强化学习），针对有标准答案的事实性问题进行自动化校验，这就像给模型配备了一个24小时的事实核查员，大幅降低“幻觉” 。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">而对于没有标准答案的开放性问题（如专业前景），则通过RLHF（基于人类反馈的强化学习），引入大量真实专家对Agent生成的方案进行打分，让模型的“品味”和“策略观”向人类专家看齐。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">正是这套笨功夫加精细活的组合，让Agent的决策不仅基于概率，更基于经过治理的、可信的知识与经验。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; letter-spacing: inherit; text-align: start; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder_err\" data-backh=\"271\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100131170\" data-ratio=\"0.4826666666666667\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4a4d3c9b-31dd-46d1-8bcb-f59f36927b00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"750\" height=\"521\" width=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"border:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;width:100%;letter-spacing:inherit;\" data-index=\"3\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVQImWNgYGBgAAAABQABh6FO1AAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\" _width=\"100%\" alt=\"图片\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 8px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; letter-spacing: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E %3Cpath d='M13.3033 5.18198C13.4986 4.98672 13.4986 4.67014 13.3033 4.47487L10.8284 2L9.9799 2.84853L11.1692 4.03784C6.58809 4.45713 3 8.30954 3 13C3 17.9706 7.02944 22 12 22C16.9706 22 21 17.9706 21 13C21 10.5147 19.9926 8.26472 18.364 6.63604L17.5154 7.48457C18.9696 8.93869 19.8 10.9021 19.8 13C19.8 17.3078 16.3078 20.8 12 20.8C7.69218 20.8 4.2 17.3078 4.2 13C4.2 8.83411 7.46585 5.43101 11.5769 5.21128L9.9799 6.80833L10.8284 7.65685L13.3033 5.18198Z' fill='%23000000' fill-opacity='0.55'/%3E %3C/svg%3E &quot;) 50% 50% / 20px no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(247, 247, 247) !important; height: 319.043px !important; width: 661px !important;\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; letter-spacing: inherit; text-align: start; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: -30px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: 16px; color: transparent; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3); overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">1</span></p>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; font-weight: bold; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: inherit; color: rgb(55, 80, 114); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">一次成功的Agent实践，与它背后的七年</strong></p>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">夸克志愿报告的成功，是在一个垂直应用场景的胜利。但在更深的层面，它更像一次路演，展示了深度研究技术落地的一种可能性。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">今天的AI行业，并不缺少聪明的产品。许多大模型应用能写诗、绘画、写代码、做复杂的逻辑推理，但在单个具体任务上，却往往缺乏稳定和可信赖的表现。用户很难将一项严肃、高风险的决策工作完全托付给它们。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">夸克的选择似乎有些逆流而动。它没有去盲目追求一个无所不能的通用助手，而是像一位手艺人，选中了高考志愿这块硬骨头，并投入了长达七年的时间去打磨。其核心，是一种被夸克称为“深度研究”的方法论。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">所谓的深度并非仅指技术，更指一种能力。它体现在对场景的深刻理解上，团队没有把志愿填报看作一个简单的概率预测问题，而是将其视为一个信息搜集、自我认知、未来规划高度交织的复杂决策系统。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">它也意味着对数据的极致治理，团队选择了一条更艰难的路——投入上百人力去做数据的线下搜集和人工校验，以此来构建Agent可信度的地基。此种深度最终落实在对模型的精细对齐上，基于海量专家数据和用户真实反馈，夸克团队不断对模型进行强化学习，让它从一个概率机器逐渐成长为一个懂得权衡、善于沟通的决策伙伴。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“志愿报告是我们对深度研究技术的一次重要实践，”蒋冠军的这句话很关键。高考场景，以其极高的复杂度和零容错的要求，成为了这套深度研究方法论的最佳试炼场。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">如今，这场高难度的路演结束了，夸克也已经推出了面向所有人的通用深度研究功能。这并非简单的功能上新，而是将那套经过千万次高压测试后被验证有效的方法论，开放给了更广泛的用户。它让普通人处理复杂信息、进行深度分析时，也能拥有一个专家级的Agent助手。</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; letter-spacing: inherit; text-align: start; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/08e360a6-37a1-4319-bf7e-7a162d375800/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder_err\" data-ratio=\"0.7506666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"750\" height=\"1536\" width=\"2048\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"422\" data-imgfileid=\"100131171\" data-original-style=\"border:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;width:100%;letter-spacing:inherit;\" data-index=\"4\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVQImWNgYGBgAAAABQABh6FO1AAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==\" _width=\"100%\" alt=\"图片\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: bottom; border-radius: 8px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; letter-spacing: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background: url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E %3Cpath d='M13.3033 5.18198C13.4986 4.98672 13.4986 4.67014 13.3033 4.47487L10.8284 2L9.9799 2.84853L11.1692 4.03784C6.58809 4.45713 3 8.30954 3 13C3 17.9706 7.02944 22 12 22C16.9706 22 21 17.9706 21 13C21 10.5147 19.9926 8.26472 18.364 6.63604L17.5154 7.48457C18.9696 8.93869 19.8 10.9021 19.8 13C19.8 17.3078 16.3078 20.8 12 20.8C7.69218 20.8 4.2 17.3078 4.2 13C4.2 8.83411 7.46585 5.43101 11.5769 5.21128L9.9799 6.80833L10.8284 7.65685L13.3033 5.18198Z' fill='%23000000' fill-opacity='0.55'/%3E %3C/svg%3E &quot;) 50% 50% / 20px no-repeat scroll padding-box border-box rgb(247, 247, 247) !important; height: 496.191px !important; width: 661px !important;\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 8px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; letter-spacing: inherit; text-align: start; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: inherit; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: -30px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: 16px; color: transparent; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3); overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">1</span></p>\n    </section>\n    <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 15px; padding: 0px 0px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; font-weight: bold; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: inherit; color: rgb(55, 80, 114); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">从解决一个真问题开始</strong></p>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">在关于AI的讨论中，我们听过太多关于颠覆和革命的宏大叙事。但夸克的故事提供了一个更朴素的视角，AI的价值，或许始于脚踏实地地解决一个真实的、具体的问题。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">它不追求成为无所不知的神，而是努力成为一个在特定领域靠谱的专家。它没有因为技术的复杂而忽视最根本的用户需求，也没有因为商业回报的不确定性而放弃对信息普惠的坚持。事实上，夸克已经连续7年为高考生和家长提供全免费、无广告的高考信息搜索和志愿填报服务。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这意味着夸克并非AI浪潮下的投机者，而是将技术落地为社会价值的长期主义者，也让今年的Agent应用更像是一场厚积薄发。超过50%的用户来自三线及以下城市 ，以及深入乡村的公益行动，都让这项技术多了一份温度。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">或许，未来真正能改变我们生活的AI，不是那个在云端不断刷新性能分数的庞然大物，而是一系列像夸克志愿报告这样，专注、深入、并真正融入我们工作与生活场景的Agent助手。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 8px 24px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; hyphens: auto; font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: inherit; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(48, 48, 48); line-height: 1.75em; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">夸克的高考故事，可能只是这个新篇章的开始。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"weui-msg\">\n  </div>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "夸克 AI 通过七年深耕的深度研究技术，在高考志愿填报这一零容错场景中实现大规模 Agent 应用落地，一个月生成千万份志愿报告",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "夸克 AI 通过七年深耕的深度研究技术，在高考志愿填报这一零容错场景中实现大规模 Agent 应用落地，一个月生成千万份志愿报告",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了阿里夸克如何在其高考志愿填报服务中应用 AI Agent 技术。面对高考志愿填报这一高复杂度、零容错的场景，夸克通过七年深耕，构建高可信度知识库（收集 8657 个权威站点、10 万份非标内容数字化，人工校验确保 99.99%准确率），并采用 SFT、RLVR 和 RLHF 等分层训练范式调校模型。特别设计了需求澄清流程等人机协作机制，使 AI 不仅能执行指令，还能处理矛盾需求（如数学差却想学计算机）。该服务在不到一个月内生成了超过 1000 万份志愿报告，其中 50%用户来自三线及以下城市，通过七年全免费服务体现了技术普惠价值。文章强调，这种'笨功夫+精细活'的方法论，展示了 AI 从玩具到工具再到智能助手的演进路径。",
